                </p>
                <p>In recent years the make-up of the benefits on offer has changed significantly and their value should not be underestimated. The focus today is increasingly on providing associates with a meaningful range of benefits that can help individuals and their dependants (where relevant) to achieve a better balance between work and home life. Whether it is maternity or paternity provisions, health screening or private healthcare coverage, or long term provisions such as your pension or income protection insurance, the bank continues to seek to develop a benefits package that promotes the health and well-being of our associates.</p>
                <p>Your total benefits package comprises a combination of core benefits and voluntary benefits.</p>
